{"tid":662710,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[全季結果速報]朱千雪蟬聯聯賽冠軍 攜手李佳芯苟芸慧晉身來季環冠盃分組賽","createTime":"2018-05-12T15:56:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T03:51:05.000Z","uid":92376,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c8ac4f0755532241f22f5ae88f4ae63a99b8e46f","tid":662710,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T15:56:24.000Z","msg":"多謝大家呢季以黎既支持,超聯已經煞科啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/yQhKdbP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FyQhKdbP.png&h=5a149076&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱千雪雖然煞科戰比李佳芯打破不敗身,但依然以三分之差達成左聯賽兩連霸,恭喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n頭三名朱千雪 李佳芯 苟芸慧晉身環冠盃分組賽<br />\n第四名既謝安琪就要參加附加賽<br />\n<br />\n至於降班方面,暫時黎講簡淑兒已經foul左,所以佢降落去冠聯果個位有可能係喺18-19季度提名新女神程序裏面空降一個新既入去,又或者由甲組果度再升多個<br />\n另外趙慧珊都因為太低分而要接受稍後既清算大會查核,由會員投票決定佢係降班定係要完全淘汰<br />\n<br />\n今季正式賽事唔計一陣甲乙組煞科戰,其餘都係得返啲升班附加賽既啫,不過都好重要架,所以大家都可以支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n冠聯附加賽 4強<br />\n首回合 <br />\n 24-5 (7)鄧麗欣vs岑麗香(4)<br />\n 25-5 (6)袁澧林vs陳嘉寶(5)<br />\n <br />\n次回合<br />\n 29-5 (4)岑麗香vs鄧麗欣(7)<br />\n 30-5 (5)陳嘉寶vs袁澧林(6)<br />\n<br />\n決賽 6月2日 凌晨<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebc71a50f300d3087f236057e221174c589c9da8","tid":662710,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T16:21:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Qpns3j2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FQpns3j2.png&h=c58bf3be&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"88bcfcde4f4ee3